After a .po file has been modified you should run

./collect-gettext-statistics.sh

to update the __catstatus.php, and submit this file to the gnubg.org website.

To update the list of translatable strings run "make gnubg.pot-update" and
"make update-po" in ../po. Then run

./collect-gettext-statistics.sh

to update the __catstatus.php, and submit this file to the gnubg.org website.

